description: 18 year old 'Chico' comes from sunny Miami, Florida. Chico is from Cuban descent and stands about 5'9' tall, weighs about 130 lbs. and has brown hair and brown eyes. And a great 7' uncut dick. By day, he's a college student studying engineering and hopes to one day be an automotive designer for one of the top automakers. 'Speed is my life, man', he told us candidly. 'I love cars. I love driving. I love driving fast. I don't like getting tickets, haha. I guess I got enough of those. But seriously, I fuckin' love cars and I know that's what I want to do with my life'.  We can't speak for the rest of his life, but we're still talking about what he did in his video! Enjoy!
title: Citiboyz 60: 'Boner Buddies', Scene #06
